parameters.name: ExperimentId
parameters.description: The ID of the HPO experiment.

parameters.name: LogName
parameters.description: The name of the log. Valid values: nnimanager.log and dispatcher.log.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The page number. Page start from page 1. If you leave this parameter empty, all content in the log file is returned.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries per page. If you leave this parameter empty, all content in the log file is returned.
